# AI Resume Analyzer

## What is AI Resume Analyzer?

AI Resume Analyzer is a Generative AI-based application that analyzes resumes using Large Language Models (LLMs) and Natural Language Processing (NLP).

The system helps users improve their resumes by:
- Extracting important information
- Evaluating ATS compatibility
- Identifying missing skills
- Suggesting improvements
- Generating interview questions

Instead of manually reviewing resumes, the AI automates the analysis process and provides intelligent recommendations.

---

## How AI Resume Analyzer Works

### 1. Resume Upload
The user uploads a resume in PDF format.

### 2. Text Extraction
The system extracts text from the uploaded resume using PDF parsers.

### 3. Text Chunking
The resume content is divided into smaller chunks for processing.

### 4. Embedding Generation
The chunks are converted into vector embeddings using embedding models.

### 5. AI Analysis
The Large Language Model analyzes:
- Skills
- Experience
- Education
- Projects
- Resume formatting

### 6. ATS Scoring
The system evaluates how ATS-friendly the resume is.

### 7. Recommendation Generation
The AI provides:
- Improvement suggestions
- Missing keywords
- Better project descriptions
- Resume optimization tips

### 8. Interview Question Generation
The system generates technical and HR interview questions based on the resume.

